{"tid":1490745,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於警察虐打人，我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-08-20T07:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:40:40.000Z","uid":46099,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d2789e966abdeee9a3654a209f969227be7819","tid":1490745,"uid":46099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"好多人集中喺兩個警員被捕一事，但其實呢件事我哋最應該關注嘅係：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察係咪仲係誠實可靠嘅證人</span><br />\n<br />\n一直以來，警察所作所為有目共睹：用私刑、砌生豬肉、選擇性執法等，佢哋所做嘅事已經同警員宣誓嘅誓詞相違背，但香港法庭一直都將香港警察當做可靠證人。<br />\n<br />\n但事實上有冇人係被警察偽造證據冤枉而入罪呢？以前嘅我唔信有，但而家我相信<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對有！</span><br />\n<br />\n兩隻黑警「被捕」，仲有千千萬萬隻每日都做緊衰嘢嘅黑警。我而家只希望從而家開始，法庭拒絕接納警方嘅證供，直至警察進行大改革同整治為止，否則法律公義無法得到伸張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40a840f9e0c7c45baddfedd7fb9ffa51bed6228","tid":1490745,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:01:30.000Z","msg":"黑警已經信唔過"},{"pid":"fd73682d46d53662a8e6b59288e2814805a96cd0","tid":1490745,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce0cb2829dfa88761ed0877bc2ad7fd7eacdc20b","tid":1490745,"uid":281973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"96868b1d4c1217e765eee3f3943752f2e3cc65c1","tid":1490745,"uid":290744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:06:56.000Z","msg":"724觀塘見"},{"pid":"53f7af445c0a276584c420c069492fd52c07e159","tid":1490745,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"【突發文宣計劃！】首個針對中立淺藍黃嘅大型文宣「牆紙」上線啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1479130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n行動post好難推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}